    "body": "fix(cuda): add device guard and runtime SM dispatch to cutlass_scaled_fp4_mm\n\nPurpose\n\nCurrently, the fp4 scaled_mm function doesn't work for the 5090 GPU, resulting in a RuntimeError: Internal Error. See https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm/issues/21274 and https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm/issues/22783 for more informatio\n\nTest Plan\n\npytest -v -s tests/kernels/quantization/test_nvfp4_scaled_mm.py\n\nTest Result\n\nAll passed.\n",
